{
  "stem": "24171.5",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Otherwise, you know, that's how I went out with the hot potatoes.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And exactly as I, kind of think, should I put another one or not?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I hear they say, [GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And about three or four officers came in.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they stopped in the front of me, because as I wanted to go with those potatoes, I always picked the place by the door.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You know?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And there I was standing.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They were burning.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I had blisters from the hot potatoes, there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I thought, if they gonna find out that they are there, they'll shoot me.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And in Plaszow, they almost-- that time, I thought, I'll be shot.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So can I go back?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Sure.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "As I was working in the-- between those military clothes, and they wore turtleneck sweaters, the gray one-- military.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I got for myself, I got for the girls, certain things [INAUDIBLE] we knitted [? over things, ?] whatever, you know.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And when we were going away, I went and I had a little shirt, small, with short sleeves.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And there was a girl, that she didn't have enough clothes for her.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I said, you put that on, whatever you want for panties or whatever, because just to [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And-- but in case, if I lose my thing, if they going to see me, that then they-- who knows?",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Then you're gonna have to give me that back.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And sure enough, when they packed us in, in the cattle cars, first underneath the skirt, I tied, again, had a little bottle with water-- again, was hanging from me, underneath the skirt.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we were [INAUDIBLE] there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "People were fainting.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So that little bottle of water went 1, 2, 3, away.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Because, you know, everybody, you know, from the things.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
